WEBVTT

01:40.450 --> 01:45.920
[Speed and Love]

01:46.289 --> 01:48.830
[Episode 27]

01:54.580 --> 01:55.700
How old is your child?

01:55.700 --> 01:56.960
Is he in kindergarten?

01:59.250 --> 02:00.090
Your child.

02:00.730 --> 02:01.860
When you came back to China,

02:01.860 --> 02:03.720
did your child come back with you?

02:05.530 --> 02:06.930
Did Jin Zhao tell you about this?

02:06.930 --> 02:08.729
He mentioned it at a dinner once.

02:13.090 --> 02:13.970
Does he

02:14.300 --> 02:15.530
talk about me often?

02:15.940 --> 02:17.570
He doesn't talk much
about his personal life,

02:17.570 --> 02:18.630
but everyone knows

02:18.650 --> 02:21.180
Mr. Jin's wife lives abroad
with their child.

02:22.020 --> 02:23.500
He said his child is quite lazy,

02:23.500 --> 02:24.700
and likes to sleep in.

02:25.300 --> 02:26.810
That's such an easy child to take care of!

02:26.810 --> 02:27.780
My sister's kid

02:27.890 --> 02:29.620
wakes up at five every morning.

02:29.650 --> 02:30.980
That's a real headache.

02:31.120 --> 02:33.180
The adults can't get any sleep, either.

02:33.180 --> 02:35.250
But my sister's daughter
has the same issue as yours—

02:35.250 --> 02:36.380
she's a picky eater.

02:36.460 --> 02:37.780
Won't eat this, won't eat that.

02:37.780 --> 02:38.980
It's so frustrating.

02:39.200 --> 02:41.090
My aunt said it's because
of poor spleen function.

02:41.090 --> 02:43.220
She took her for therapeutic massage.

02:43.570 --> 02:44.900
You could try that, too.

02:47.500 --> 02:49.829
You're the one with poor spleen function.

02:55.920 --> 02:57.850
Wife? Child?

02:58.450 --> 03:00.050
You've made up quite a story.

03:08.890 --> 03:11.690
According to you,
I'm both a mother and a daughter—

03:11.690 --> 03:13.150
playing two roles at once.

03:13.570 --> 03:15.970
What exactly have you been telling people?

03:17.900 --> 03:19.570
Now your lazy, picky little baby

03:19.570 --> 03:20.340
is angry.

03:20.500 --> 03:22.500
Don't you need to explain yourself?

03:30.060 --> 03:30.650
I'm busy.

03:31.000 --> 03:31.690
Later.

05:00.220 --> 05:01.420
Why did you come back?

05:04.810 --> 05:06.940
I heard there was a child who was upset.

05:07.480 --> 05:08.810
I'm here to comfort her.

05:10.620 --> 05:12.420
Is this how you comfort someone?

05:15.760 --> 05:18.090
How would you like me to comfort you, then?

05:19.640 --> 05:20.690
You've really changed now.

05:20.690 --> 05:21.860
You weren't like this before.

05:21.860 --> 05:24.120
You used to pull me into alleys
and tell me

05:24.240 --> 05:26.370
that girls shouldn't behave this way.

05:26.580 --> 05:28.540
Back then,
you were still immature.

05:28.540 --> 05:30.270
Don't give me that parent talk.

06:06.230 --> 06:07.860
Look at the axis.

06:07.890 --> 06:09.420
From here to here, it's 30.

06:09.450 --> 06:11.180
Does it matter if it exceeds 30?

06:26.540 --> 06:27.780
Thank you, Senior.

06:28.100 --> 06:29.740
Here, try it.

06:29.890 --> 06:32.020
I waited in line to buy you this coffee.

06:32.540 --> 06:34.210
Their coffee is award-winning.

06:34.210 --> 06:35.659
I queued up at 4 or 5 a.m.

06:35.690 --> 06:37.020
I queued for a long time.

06:37.250 --> 06:38.010
Why did you only buy one for him?

06:38.010 --> 06:38.740
I don't get one?

06:38.740 --> 06:39.860
So what?

06:39.890 --> 06:40.980
-You are so biased—
-Here.

06:40.980 --> 06:41.840
You can have it.

06:42.570 --> 06:44.180
Senior, you're too nice.

06:44.250 --> 06:45.330
He likes me.

06:45.420 --> 06:47.370
We are close, right?

06:47.620 --> 06:48.210
Senior.

06:48.500 --> 06:49.500
Is there something wrong

06:49.500 --> 06:51.300
with this diagram's wheelbase?

06:51.370 --> 06:53.130
Don't you know this?
It was taught in class.

06:53.130 --> 06:53.790
Let me do it.

06:54.060 --> 06:54.690
It's so easy.

06:54.690 --> 06:55.770
Don't you know?

06:55.860 --> 06:57.180
Tell him. Yes, tell him.

06:57.180 --> 06:58.860
Look at this point and this point.

06:58.860 --> 06:59.250
Yes.

06:59.330 --> 07:00.010
That one.

07:00.100 --> 07:02.030
-Let me tell you.
-The blackboard.

07:04.170 --> 07:04.780
Mu!

07:08.320 --> 07:09.250
Why are you here?

07:09.570 --> 07:11.170
Without telling me, either.

07:12.810 --> 07:14.210
I'm here to tell you that

07:14.300 --> 07:15.740
I've received the notice of employment.

07:15.740 --> 07:16.620
From today onwards,

07:16.620 --> 07:19.130
I'm a full-time employee
of the research institute.

07:19.130 --> 07:20.390
Notice of employment?

07:20.890 --> 07:21.740
Show me.

07:24.100 --> 07:24.830
No.

07:32.180 --> 07:34.100
Not unless you hug me.

07:34.750 --> 07:36.280
Don't you see where we are?

07:37.740 --> 07:39.190
What? Does your school

07:39.210 --> 07:41.100
have rules against dating?

07:48.370 --> 07:49.700
You're acting strange.

07:50.330 --> 07:51.100
What's strange about me?

07:51.100 --> 07:52.210
I'm wondering when

07:52.210 --> 07:54.370
you'll buy me a coffee, too.

07:55.310 --> 07:57.010
Zhao, is this your girlfriend?

07:57.010 --> 07:58.270
Never seen her before.

08:00.940 --> 08:01.450
Yes.

08:01.860 --> 08:03.180
She's usually quite busy.

08:03.180 --> 08:04.010
She finally found some time

08:04.010 --> 08:05.670
to grace me with her presence.

08:06.640 --> 08:07.960
Alright, we're heading out first, then.

08:07.960 --> 08:09.160
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

08:12.480 --> 08:14.340
Does that short-haired girl like you?

08:14.340 --> 08:15.920
Why did she only buy coffee for you

08:15.920 --> 08:17.250
and not for anyone else?

08:24.370 --> 08:25.690
They came to discuss

08:25.690 --> 08:27.250
fluid mechanics with me

08:27.810 --> 08:29.570
and to ask about admissions.

08:35.610 --> 08:37.330
I run a coffee shop myself.

08:38.289 --> 08:40.090
Isn't the coffee at home good enough?

08:40.090 --> 08:42.150
Why bother drinking someone else's?

09:04.670 --> 09:05.520
Behave yourself.

09:05.520 --> 09:07.010
Don't you see where we are?

09:10.780 --> 09:13.380
Our school doesn't have rules
against dating.

09:28.700 --> 09:30.630
Am I coming to dinner tonight, too?

09:31.480 --> 09:32.300
With whom?

09:33.190 --> 09:35.120
You'll find out when you get there.

09:36.210 --> 09:37.260
Who is it?

10:00.440 --> 10:01.550
What's the rush?

10:03.510 --> 10:04.430
Come here!

10:05.940 --> 10:07.570
Is there something wrong with your eyes?

10:07.570 --> 10:08.300
Look.

10:08.390 --> 10:09.540
My angle is so tight here.

10:09.540 --> 10:10.960
And then you parked your car sideways.

10:10.960 --> 10:12.490
How am I supposed to back up?

10:14.060 --> 10:16.520
I'll go handle this.
You go up and wait for me.

10:20.380 --> 10:21.170
Hey, Ma'am, I...

10:21.170 --> 10:22.430
What do you mean "hey"?

10:22.960 --> 10:24.060
I know that look on your face.

10:24.060 --> 10:25.600
Are you discriminating against
female drivers?

10:25.600 --> 10:27.660
Let me tell you, I can sue you for this.

10:27.730 --> 10:29.380
It's him who blocked this spot,

10:29.380 --> 10:31.510
making it impossible for me to back up.

10:31.720 --> 10:34.080
Why are you honking?

10:36.780 --> 10:38.140
It's because he parked sideways here—

10:38.140 --> 10:38.720
let me tell you.

10:38.720 --> 10:39.790
Come and judge for yourself.

10:39.790 --> 10:41.190
Wen, move your car first.

10:43.670 --> 10:44.870
I'll help you back up.

10:46.710 --> 10:47.380
Alright.

12:53.260 --> 12:54.180
Sanlai!

12:54.540 --> 12:55.970
Jiang Mu?

12:56.260 --> 12:57.350
What are you doing here?

12:57.350 --> 12:58.190
Oh my God!

12:58.940 --> 12:59.810
Long time no see.

12:59.810 --> 13:01.260
Long time no see.

13:03.900 --> 13:04.660
Our Jiang Mu

13:04.660 --> 13:06.660
is getting more and more beautiful.

13:07.690 --> 13:08.850
Just good makeup.

13:10.020 --> 13:10.950
Where's Brandy?

13:11.450 --> 13:12.710
He went to park the car.

13:12.810 --> 13:13.540
Park?

13:13.980 --> 13:16.040
He can handle the steering wheel now?

13:18.980 --> 13:19.710
That's good.

13:19.800 --> 13:21.160
Anyway, now that you're here with him,

13:21.160 --> 13:23.090
encourage him to drive more often.

13:24.140 --> 13:25.600
Who are you chatting with?

13:26.680 --> 13:28.720
Oh my God! Isn't this my lil' sis?

13:29.100 --> 13:30.020
Crazy?

13:30.630 --> 13:31.850
You've really grown up!

13:31.850 --> 13:33.050
You've become so pretty!

13:33.050 --> 13:34.370
-I almost didn't recognize you.
-Take it easy.

13:34.370 --> 13:35.730
You've changed a lot, too.

13:35.730 --> 13:36.610
More mature, right?

13:36.610 --> 13:38.010
More weathered, I'd say.

13:38.180 --> 13:39.710
What are you talking about?

13:42.410 --> 13:43.530
When did you two get in touch?

13:43.530 --> 13:44.790
Why didn't you tell us?

13:46.170 --> 13:47.170
It's been a while.

13:48.280 --> 13:50.000
Don't just stand there.
Let's sit down and talk.

13:50.000 --> 13:50.600
Okay.

13:53.450 --> 13:54.570
How long has it been since we last met?

13:54.570 --> 13:56.260
Today, I've got to drink with Mu.

13:56.260 --> 13:56.970
Yes.

13:57.050 --> 13:58.310
She won't be drinking.

13:59.570 --> 14:00.970
It made sense
when you protected her at 18.

14:00.970 --> 14:01.900
But you're still doing it now.

14:01.900 --> 14:03.900
Won't you let us get a little closer?

14:04.280 --> 14:05.250
I'm in a good mood today.

14:05.250 --> 14:07.510
If Mu doesn't drink, the three of us will.

14:08.980 --> 14:10.440
I'm not drinking, either.

14:11.210 --> 14:12.540
Just the two of us, then.

14:12.780 --> 14:13.470
Waiter!

14:13.990 --> 14:14.850
Bring the food!

14:17.060 --> 14:18.790
After what happened to Brandy,

14:18.850 --> 14:20.710
I completely cut ties with Wan's.

14:22.170 --> 14:22.860
But anyway,

14:23.010 --> 14:24.970
Crazy handled this matter properly.

14:24.970 --> 14:26.570
This shows that in his heart,

14:26.970 --> 14:28.300
he still cares about us.

14:29.300 --> 14:31.450
Can you stop being so sappy?

14:31.940 --> 14:33.060
I just felt guilty.

14:35.490 --> 14:37.240
I was careless with what happened

14:37.240 --> 14:38.120
with Iron Cock,

14:39.080 --> 14:40.010
hurting Brandy.

14:41.420 --> 14:42.140
It's okay.

14:42.780 --> 14:44.380
Being alive is what matters.

14:46.060 --> 14:47.900
He suffered for a few years.

14:48.300 --> 14:50.160
But thankfully
Crazy was there at the time.

14:50.160 --> 14:51.130
He's big enough

14:51.280 --> 14:52.710
and helped me take care of Brandy,

14:52.710 --> 14:53.970
making things easier.

14:54.100 --> 14:55.550
I barely took care of him for a few days.

14:55.550 --> 14:57.920
As soon as he felt a little better,
he wanted to take the self-study exam,

14:57.920 --> 14:59.250
dragging me along, too.

14:59.340 --> 15:01.210
Come on, you have the nerve to complain?

15:01.210 --> 15:02.960
Do you know why he took you with him?

15:02.960 --> 15:03.800
He was sick

15:03.830 --> 15:05.330
and you were making all that noise
playing video games.

15:05.330 --> 15:06.410
It was bothering him.

15:06.410 --> 15:08.670
I've never liked studying
since I was a kid.

15:08.670 --> 15:10.970
After middle school,
I just became a slacker.

15:10.970 --> 15:12.420
Absolutely ungrateful.

15:12.470 --> 15:13.490
If it weren't for Brandy,

15:13.490 --> 15:15.490
would you be a college graduate now?

15:15.610 --> 15:17.520
Brandy originally wanted to drag him along
to take the graduate exam.

15:17.520 --> 15:19.790
This guy threatened to kill himself,

15:19.940 --> 15:21.300
so Brandy finally let him off the hook.

15:21.300 --> 15:23.060
Look, at my age,

15:23.690 --> 15:25.570
I'm satisfied

15:25.850 --> 15:27.570
just getting a college degree.

15:27.570 --> 15:29.230
You really should be content.

15:29.660 --> 15:30.810
Crazy is doing well now.

15:30.810 --> 15:32.520
He's working as a technician under Brandy.

15:32.520 --> 15:34.320
His life has some stability now.

15:35.810 --> 15:38.040
However, he still hasn't found

15:38.060 --> 15:39.420
a partner...

15:40.450 --> 15:41.050
Jiang Mu,

15:41.650 --> 15:43.500
help Crazy find someone good.

15:43.890 --> 15:45.690
Mu, I'm counting on you for this.

15:45.890 --> 15:47.420
These two aren't reliable.

15:48.090 --> 15:49.680
No problem. Leave it to me.

15:52.880 --> 15:55.240
Sanlai, don't just talk about Crazy Jin.

15:55.260 --> 15:56.170
Tell us about yourself.

15:56.170 --> 15:58.370
How have you been doing all these years?

16:01.140 --> 16:02.380
Just by looking at me

16:02.380 --> 16:04.180
you can tell I'm doing very well.

16:04.850 --> 16:05.570
However,

16:05.970 --> 16:07.660
when Brandy left back then,

16:07.800 --> 16:08.760
Xishi died, too.

16:08.900 --> 16:10.140
I was quite heartbroken.

16:10.140 --> 16:10.970
So I thought

16:10.970 --> 16:12.610
I'd close down the pet shop.

16:13.110 --> 16:14.500
Later I opened a fast food restaurant.

16:14.500 --> 16:16.530
Business is still pretty good, though.

16:16.530 --> 16:18.660
So that fast food restaurant is yours?

16:19.140 --> 16:20.200
You've been there?

16:21.300 --> 16:22.180
I didn't go in.

16:22.600 --> 16:24.610
I saw it when I returned
during my first vacation

16:24.610 --> 16:26.010
when I studied in Canada.

16:37.130 --> 16:37.930
You know what?

16:38.090 --> 16:40.060
I'm truly a business genius.

16:40.430 --> 16:41.450
When I opened that fast food restaurant,

16:41.450 --> 16:43.060
I made quite a bit of money
after a few years.

16:43.060 --> 16:45.260
But later I realized
without my bros around me,

16:45.260 --> 16:46.520
life was really tough.

16:46.560 --> 16:48.210
So I leased out the restaurant

16:48.210 --> 16:49.570
and came back to join Brandy.

16:49.570 --> 16:50.490
This guy

16:50.730 --> 16:52.530
rushed back here in such a hurry.

16:52.810 --> 16:55.060
He opened a fast food restaurant
right at the factory entrance.

16:55.060 --> 16:56.890
When he first opened,
there was no business at all.

16:56.890 --> 16:58.560
If it weren't for all of us

16:58.750 --> 16:59.610
supporting him,

16:59.610 --> 17:02.010
I tell you,
he would've gone under long ago.

17:02.300 --> 17:03.610
Plus, Brandy

17:03.970 --> 17:05.099
had some influence.

17:05.250 --> 17:06.380
More and more people

17:06.470 --> 17:07.730
started eating at his place

17:07.730 --> 17:08.970
instead of the cafeteria.

17:08.970 --> 17:10.819
He even borrowed my savings.

17:11.660 --> 17:13.010
Saying he wanted to expand the business.

17:13.010 --> 17:14.720
Made it so our cafeteria
couldn't even stay in business.

17:14.720 --> 17:15.859
Our boss had a real problem with him.

17:15.859 --> 17:17.099
That's enough.

17:17.579 --> 17:18.800
Are you getting old?

17:18.819 --> 17:20.710
Why are you so talkative?

17:20.730 --> 17:22.099
Who borrowed money from you?

17:22.099 --> 17:23.300
Don't talk nonsense.

17:23.490 --> 17:24.490
Let me summarize.

17:24.690 --> 17:26.099
So this factory

17:26.130 --> 17:28.010
wanted to change their cafeteria operator.

17:28.010 --> 17:28.920
So I submitted a bid.

17:28.920 --> 17:30.010
Surprisingly, many of the managers

17:30.010 --> 17:31.490
had eaten at my restaurant before

17:31.490 --> 17:32.290
and gave me the opportunity,

17:32.290 --> 17:33.290
and they chose me.

17:33.290 --> 17:34.420
Give me a break.

17:34.690 --> 17:36.890
It's thanks to that glib tongue of yours

17:36.940 --> 17:38.450
that you secured the contract.

17:38.450 --> 17:39.340
That's enough.

17:39.730 --> 17:41.150
Speaking of which, I just remembered.

17:41.150 --> 17:42.770
Are you tired? Would you like some water?

17:42.770 --> 17:43.420
Well.

17:43.450 --> 17:45.710
Let me formally introduce myself again.

17:45.820 --> 17:46.770
I'm now

17:46.770 --> 17:47.970
a man with a business card.

17:47.970 --> 17:49.370
I'm a Cafeteria Manager.

17:54.950 --> 17:55.550
All right.

17:58.530 --> 17:59.580
So you're

17:59.580 --> 18:01.780
planning to stay in Nanjing from now on?

18:02.730 --> 18:04.120
Yeah, just like you.

18:04.750 --> 18:06.010
Clinging onto Brandy.

18:06.010 --> 18:07.250
I can see that.

18:07.640 --> 18:08.990
You do that yourself.

18:09.010 --> 18:10.820
-Why is it your name on this?
-I won't cling onto him.

18:10.820 --> 18:11.820
You only have Brandy.

18:11.820 --> 18:13.610
-You don't even have a partner.
-I didn't write it.

18:13.610 --> 18:15.400
You really know how to hit a sore spot,
don't you?

18:15.400 --> 18:16.810
What about it?

18:16.830 --> 18:17.820
-You, too.
-Stop talking.

18:17.820 --> 18:18.420
Come on, have a drink.

18:18.420 --> 18:19.210
Come on.

18:19.240 --> 18:21.140
I'll just drink water for now
and make it up next time.

18:21.140 --> 18:21.690
Fine, you owe us one.

18:21.690 --> 18:23.690
-When will you make it up?
-I owe you.

18:27.920 --> 18:29.520
We've been apart for so long.

18:29.670 --> 18:30.800
Yet in this reunion,

18:31.010 --> 18:33.050
we're still as close as before.

18:33.610 --> 18:36.370
It's like time hasn't passed at all.

18:38.900 --> 18:41.380
Sanlai is still as eloquent as before,

18:41.860 --> 18:43.290
talking non-stop.

18:43.940 --> 18:44.970
And there's still the jumpy Crazy,

18:44.970 --> 18:46.900
who loves to bicker with Sanlai.

18:47.750 --> 18:48.560
It's just that

18:49.050 --> 18:51.580
Sanlai has become more composed
than before.

18:51.770 --> 18:53.960
And Crazy's hair has gone from red

18:54.110 --> 18:55.270
to black.

18:56.340 --> 18:58.300
When Zhao is with them,

18:58.730 --> 19:00.170
though he doesn't say much,

19:00.170 --> 19:01.410
you can tell

19:01.720 --> 19:03.320
he's at peace and is content.

19:04.140 --> 19:05.180
Perhaps now,

19:05.610 --> 19:08.370
few people know about his tumultuous past.

19:08.920 --> 19:10.920
Only in front of these old friends,

19:11.800 --> 19:13.330
he's still the same Brandy.

19:18.330 --> 19:18.960
I quit.

19:20.750 --> 19:21.440
You quit?

19:25.660 --> 19:27.920
You're not trying to have a baby, are you?

19:29.140 --> 19:30.180
Are you really planning to wait

19:30.180 --> 19:31.480
until your kid is grown up
and running around

19:31.480 --> 19:32.540
before telling us?

19:33.010 --> 19:34.410
It hasn't been that long,

19:34.560 --> 19:36.190
just

19:37.520 --> 19:38.920
a little over two months.

19:41.570 --> 19:43.090
Brandy! Look at you.

19:43.860 --> 19:44.660
It's not like we never met

19:44.660 --> 19:47.140
or had meals together during these two months.

19:47.140 --> 19:47.770
Your mouth seems

19:47.770 --> 19:49.500
like it's been padlocked shut.

19:50.040 --> 19:51.630
Don't act like an old nanny.

19:52.050 --> 19:53.010
I can't be giving you

19:53.010 --> 19:55.670
every single life update by calling you,
right?

19:55.850 --> 19:58.650
That day I called you
during Mid-Autumn Festival,

19:59.350 --> 20:01.680
that girl on the phone was Jiang Mu,
right?

20:02.590 --> 20:04.590
You two were already together then?

20:05.850 --> 20:06.980
Not yet at that time.

20:09.820 --> 20:10.490
Fine!

20:11.770 --> 20:12.770
No wonder lately

20:12.770 --> 20:14.570
I could never get you to hang out.

20:14.660 --> 20:15.450
Every time we met,

20:15.450 --> 20:17.530
you acted like you had firecrackers
under your butt—

20:17.530 --> 20:18.730
barely sitting down before leaving.

20:18.730 --> 20:21.130
So you were rushing back
to be with Jiang Mu.

20:23.530 --> 20:24.990
It's the honeymoon phase.

20:25.380 --> 20:26.900
Yeah, right!

20:27.210 --> 20:30.010
What kind of honeymoon phase
lasts for so many years?

20:30.010 --> 20:31.410
Isn't that nice, though?

20:31.920 --> 20:32.850
Zhao and Mu.

20:35.090 --> 20:35.770
Tell me,

20:36.770 --> 20:38.170
how far have you two gone?

20:40.970 --> 20:42.030
I want to marry her.

20:42.290 --> 20:44.250
Jin and I were

20:44.690 --> 20:45.620
discussing this the other day—

20:45.620 --> 20:47.380
saying if either of us got married,

20:47.380 --> 20:48.280
you'd be left alone.

20:48.280 --> 20:50.680
We were just thinking
how pitiful you'd be.

20:51.010 --> 20:52.340
And now you're telling me

20:52.340 --> 20:53.820
you want to get married?

20:58.540 --> 20:59.600
Put your hand down.

21:03.590 --> 21:05.850
Back then,
when you changed your number,

21:06.490 --> 21:09.050
why did you persuade me
to change mine too,

21:09.180 --> 21:10.980
not letting me contact Jiang Mu?

21:11.060 --> 21:13.050
That was because at that time...

21:13.050 --> 21:14.660
You haven't been

21:16.170 --> 21:18.770
guarding against me all these years,
have you?

21:20.590 --> 21:24.070
You knew how handsome and charming I am,

21:24.490 --> 21:25.210
and you were afraid Jiang Mu

21:25.210 --> 21:27.600
might fall for me
if she contacted me too much.

21:27.600 --> 21:28.250
Right?

21:29.470 --> 21:30.150
Yes.

21:30.610 --> 21:32.010
I was just jealous of you.

21:33.680 --> 21:35.440
I get jealous of any man

21:35.900 --> 21:36.670
who appears around Mu.

21:36.670 --> 21:37.530
You're just love-obsessed.

21:37.530 --> 21:38.490
I am love-obsessed.

21:38.490 --> 21:39.290
You're no fun.

21:43.150 --> 21:43.950
Wait a second.

21:44.970 --> 21:46.630
If you get married, do I have to

21:46.850 --> 21:48.180
give two wedding gifts?

21:48.720 --> 21:50.860
Two, three, four, five gifts are all fine.

21:50.860 --> 21:51.590
Be generous.

21:54.900 --> 21:56.500
Something up at the company?

21:58.990 --> 22:00.520
Okay, I'll head back first.

22:06.530 --> 22:08.920
During the first two years
I was studying in Canada,

22:08.920 --> 22:11.380
I returned to Manshi
every vacation to look for you.

22:11.380 --> 22:12.440
But what about you?

22:12.530 --> 22:13.690
Not a word from you.

22:15.100 --> 22:16.340
I was so angry.

22:16.490 --> 22:19.020
I swore I would never go back
to find you again.

22:19.490 --> 22:20.690
Here, don't be angry.

22:25.620 --> 22:26.450
But who knew?

22:26.880 --> 22:29.880
In the third and fourth year,
I still couldn't resist.

22:32.830 --> 22:33.660
Do you know

22:34.160 --> 22:35.530
which time
left the deepest impression

22:35.530 --> 22:36.690
on me?

22:39.210 --> 22:40.530
Once at the airport,

22:40.940 --> 22:42.490
I lost my laptop bag.

22:42.730 --> 22:44.050
It wasn't the laptop that mattered,

22:44.050 --> 22:46.910
but the keychain
you gave me that was attached to it.

22:48.660 --> 22:50.690
I searched frantically everywhere,

22:50.690 --> 22:51.940
but couldn't find it anywhere.

22:51.940 --> 22:53.250
I was almost in tears.

22:55.100 --> 22:56.380
Fortunately, in the end,

22:56.380 --> 22:58.910
a cleaning lady found it
and returned it to me.

23:00.770 --> 23:02.370
Thank goodness it was found.

23:12.880 --> 23:14.080
I'm glad you found it.

23:18.790 --> 23:19.790
It was my fault.

23:20.820 --> 23:21.900
I made you suffer.

23:24.570 --> 23:26.050
So you do know I suffered.

23:31.210 --> 23:33.010
How do you plan to make it up to me?

23:39.900 --> 23:42.100
How would you like me
to make it up to you?

23:54.480 --> 23:55.810
What are you guys doing?

24:15.440 --> 24:17.040
Would you like some red wine?

24:17.040 --> 24:17.840
No, thanks.

24:19.130 --> 24:20.930
The airplane food was terrible.

24:21.290 --> 24:22.130
I'm starving.

24:25.640 --> 24:26.240
Here.

24:28.290 --> 24:29.150
Egg fried rice.

24:30.050 --> 24:31.260
His fried rice is amazing.

24:31.260 --> 24:32.520
Aren't you having any?

24:32.770 --> 24:33.810
You go ahead.

24:34.400 --> 24:35.290
What a shame.

24:37.770 --> 24:40.170
No one loves egg fried rice
as much as you do.

24:40.250 --> 24:41.580
Mind your own business.

24:52.180 --> 24:53.690
I won't stay long this time.

24:53.690 --> 24:55.740
I won't intrude
on your private time together.

24:55.740 --> 24:56.670
It's your place.

24:57.130 --> 24:58.060
Do as you please.

24:58.420 --> 24:59.370
His place?

24:59.660 --> 25:00.730
To be precise,

25:00.890 --> 25:02.350
it's a company apartment.

25:02.450 --> 25:04.770
But occasionally when I'm here
on business, I stay here

25:04.770 --> 25:05.580
and annoy him.

25:07.130 --> 25:08.100
Annoying indeed.

25:08.100 --> 25:09.300
Then don't stay here.

25:09.570 --> 25:10.570
Then stop eating.

25:11.370 --> 25:12.630
Let him finish eating.

25:15.210 --> 25:15.860
Sit down.

25:19.580 --> 25:20.580
He came to Nanjing

25:20.770 --> 25:22.700
even before his injury had healed.

25:22.800 --> 25:24.000
No one could stop him.

25:24.820 --> 25:26.350
I didn't know why back then,

25:26.450 --> 25:27.490
but now...

25:30.530 --> 25:31.730
I think I understand.

25:33.050 --> 25:34.180
If it weren't for me,

25:34.370 --> 25:35.970
you would have lost that leg.

25:38.240 --> 25:39.370
You can have it back.

25:41.250 --> 25:42.140
You know

25:42.640 --> 25:43.920
that's not what I want.

25:47.580 --> 25:49.180
There are things I have to do.

25:50.840 --> 25:52.570
It would trouble me otherwise.

25:53.460 --> 25:55.520
That's why I had to return to Nanjing.

25:58.840 --> 25:59.560
Jin Zhao.

26:00.230 --> 26:01.120
Will you...

26:02.900 --> 26:04.690
ever drive again?

26:22.320 --> 26:23.720
How have you been lately?

26:23.940 --> 26:25.140
Are you feeling better?

26:25.140 --> 26:25.870
Much better.

26:25.920 --> 26:28.180
I even walked for half an hour yesterday.

26:30.620 --> 26:32.550
You owe me a big favor.

26:33.770 --> 26:34.970
How should I repay it?

26:39.180 --> 26:40.440
I haven't decided yet.

26:40.530 --> 26:42.420
What I wanted most was

26:42.580 --> 26:44.660
to have one good race against you.

26:44.690 --> 26:45.450
But

26:45.660 --> 26:47.860
with your current physical condition,

26:48.000 --> 26:48.960
honestly,

26:49.380 --> 26:50.290
I think

26:50.490 --> 26:52.550
you're pretty much done with racing.

26:55.690 --> 26:57.220
Thank you for your honesty.

26:58.720 --> 26:59.680
So,

27:00.450 --> 27:02.250
what are you planning to do next?

27:02.620 --> 27:03.690
I'm not sure yet.

27:05.660 --> 27:07.660
I definitely can't just do nothing.

27:08.200 --> 27:10.260
Since I can't race anymore, maybe...

27:10.520 --> 27:11.850
I'll finish my studies.

27:12.620 --> 27:13.680
I'll go study cars.

27:15.970 --> 27:17.210
Interesting idea.

27:19.530 --> 27:20.610
Mu

27:24.010 --> 27:26.610
has always wanted me
to finish my studies, too.

27:26.810 --> 27:27.640
Jiang Mu?

27:29.650 --> 27:32.110
You haven't been in touch with her,
have you?

27:36.570 --> 27:37.570
Like you said,

27:38.130 --> 27:40.130
my body will never be the same again.

27:40.560 --> 27:42.280
Mu should find someone...

27:43.950 --> 27:45.150
healthier

27:46.070 --> 27:47.330
to spend her life with.

27:49.010 --> 27:50.420
I think

27:52.570 --> 27:54.430
you're making decisions for her.

27:57.450 --> 27:58.100
However,

27:58.800 --> 28:00.400
I still respect your choice.

28:07.520 --> 28:09.780
My club needs someone in a core position.

28:10.180 --> 28:11.620
I now believe

28:12.050 --> 28:14.190
the most important quality
for that position

28:14.190 --> 28:16.320
isn't necessarily speed on the track.

28:17.070 --> 28:18.110
My club

28:18.480 --> 28:19.640
is still open to you.

28:20.080 --> 28:21.340
You're welcome to join

28:22.100 --> 28:22.970
anytime.

28:25.130 --> 28:25.920
We'll see.

28:28.770 --> 28:31.290
I gave him a condition at that time.

28:33.820 --> 28:34.750
What condition?

28:35.130 --> 28:36.290
I invested in a

28:36.490 --> 28:37.940
racing club.

28:38.440 --> 28:41.130
Asked him to mentor
the young people in the club,

28:41.230 --> 28:43.230
and share his experience with them.

28:45.040 --> 28:47.430
No wonder you often go on business trips.

28:49.620 --> 28:50.820
He's a partner

28:51.490 --> 28:52.660
at the club.

28:56.010 --> 28:57.620
An exploited partner.

28:59.310 --> 29:00.860
You have no idea how long I begged him

29:00.860 --> 29:02.390
before he agreed to help me.

29:03.680 --> 29:04.440
Enough.

29:06.040 --> 29:07.970
What are you really here for today?

29:13.370 --> 29:15.410
Jin Zhao, do you want to

29:16.680 --> 29:18.640
return to the team and drive for me?

29:28.730 --> 29:29.970
I've asked Dr. Julia.

29:29.970 --> 29:32.620
She said your body has recovered now,

29:32.960 --> 29:35.370
so you can try driving again.

29:36.110 --> 29:37.030
As long as

29:38.800 --> 29:41.260
you overcome your psychological barriers.

30:19.150 --> 30:20.170
Taking compromising photos of me?

30:20.170 --> 30:23.100
Now I have leverage over you.

30:23.720 --> 30:25.770
For the next few questions I ask,

30:26.050 --> 30:27.780
you'd better answer honestly.

30:28.250 --> 30:29.580
What do you want to know?

30:31.770 --> 30:34.030
Hearing from Sanlai and Crazy Jin today,

30:34.160 --> 30:37.420
I'm very curious about
what you've been doing these 6 years.

30:37.420 --> 30:38.880
I spent a few years abroad,

30:39.180 --> 30:40.340
then came back to China.

30:40.340 --> 30:41.580
When you were abroad,

30:42.000 --> 30:43.130
who were you with?

30:43.490 --> 30:44.140
Sanlai

30:44.680 --> 30:45.480
and Crazy Jin.

30:45.820 --> 30:46.620
Who else?

30:50.580 --> 30:52.210
Tell me the truth.

30:56.290 --> 30:57.450
Did Sanlai

30:58.380 --> 30:59.580
contact you?

31:01.800 --> 31:03.840
Yes, I had some free time today

31:04.160 --> 31:05.680
and caught up with Sanlai.

31:09.380 --> 31:11.110
I just spent a few years abroad.

31:11.640 --> 31:13.110
The medical technology there is better.

31:13.110 --> 31:14.710
I came back after treatment.

31:15.680 --> 31:17.610
Answer me properly. With whom?

31:20.100 --> 31:20.860
No one.

31:21.080 --> 31:23.110
Look at you, hesitating to speak.

31:23.440 --> 31:25.500
You don't have another woman, do you?

31:26.450 --> 31:27.050
No.

31:27.660 --> 31:28.340
Look.

31:28.690 --> 31:29.900
You didn't deny it right away.

31:29.900 --> 31:30.820
You hesitated.

31:31.130 --> 31:33.930
You're not answering me.
You're not being honest.

31:41.300 --> 31:42.410
I'm up.

31:45.920 --> 31:46.640
Where is he?

31:56.530 --> 31:57.730
Where did he go?

32:02.970 --> 32:08.730
[We're out to buy breakfast. Wait for me.]

32:42.210 --> 32:43.340
Don't block the way!

32:44.620 --> 32:46.510
Why are you blocking? So annoying.

32:46.510 --> 32:47.610
Sorry.

32:49.100 --> 32:50.690
Save me a spot!

32:59.010 --> 33:00.410
Are you always this crazy

33:00.480 --> 33:02.050
when grocery shopping?

33:03.380 --> 33:04.910
It's not usually like this.

33:09.530 --> 33:10.490
Are you done?

33:13.630 --> 33:14.230
This one

33:14.570 --> 33:15.400
looks good.

33:17.490 --> 33:18.490
Not fresh enough.

33:23.010 --> 33:24.270
The potatoes are good.

33:24.940 --> 33:27.340
Green pepper and
shredded potatoes would work.

33:27.340 --> 33:28.230
Shredded potatoes are fine,

33:28.230 --> 33:29.180
but not green peppers.

33:29.180 --> 33:30.910
Mu doesn't like green peppers.

33:33.470 --> 33:34.350
Ma'am, please weigh these.

33:34.350 --> 33:34.980
Here.

33:37.630 --> 33:38.990
-Pork ribs.
-2.80 yuan.

33:39.230 --> 33:40.360
You're buying more?

33:41.090 --> 33:42.490
Young man, 2.80.

33:44.340 --> 33:45.060
Okay.

33:45.830 --> 33:47.200
Sir, please weigh these ribs.

33:47.200 --> 33:48.050
Sure.

33:49.350 --> 33:50.350
Is the meat fresh?

33:50.440 --> 33:51.400
Very fresh.

33:52.970 --> 33:54.430
How much longer will we be?

33:54.490 --> 33:55.050
Almost done.

33:55.050 --> 33:57.210
Weren't you the one
who wanted to come along?

33:57.210 --> 33:59.210
But I didn't expect this situation.

33:59.270 --> 34:00.930
Wait a moment. One last thing.

34:02.920 --> 34:03.710
Farm eggs.

34:03.990 --> 34:04.580
Farm eggs?

34:04.580 --> 34:06.710
-Sir, you haven't paid!
-What is that?

34:07.100 --> 34:07.770
Pay up.

34:08.560 --> 34:09.780
Pay over there with the QR code.

34:09.780 --> 34:10.650
Okay.

34:30.250 --> 34:30.810
Weigh these.

34:30.810 --> 34:31.440
Okay.

34:35.860 --> 34:36.790
Potatoes, eggs.

34:37.610 --> 34:38.219
Got them.

34:38.370 --> 34:39.179
Ribs.

34:39.830 --> 34:40.460
Got it.

34:40.739 --> 34:42.739
Cabbage, eggplant, cilantro.

34:42.900 --> 34:43.699
Got them.

34:44.340 --> 34:45.610
Edamame, cucumber.

34:46.130 --> 34:47.090
Got them.

34:47.449 --> 34:50.820
Green onions, lettuce, oranges, bananas.

34:50.820 --> 34:51.570
Got everything?

34:51.570 --> 34:52.420
Yes.

34:57.970 --> 34:59.300
What are you smiling at?

35:01.220 --> 35:02.550
You're acting strange.

35:04.480 --> 35:05.790
How am I acting strange?

35:05.790 --> 35:07.190
You're not planning

35:07.790 --> 35:08.980
to marry Mu, are you?

35:13.410 --> 35:15.100
[Epilogue]

35:16.050 --> 35:16.780
Excuse me.

35:16.810 --> 35:18.180
Have you seen

35:18.340 --> 35:18.890
a keychain?

35:18.890 --> 35:20.220
-How does it look like?
-I really need help to find it.

35:20.220 --> 35:21.770
It's... It's about this big.

35:21.770 --> 35:23.900
-With four Chinese characters on it.
-Oh, okay.

35:23.900 --> 35:24.740
Please, you have to help me.

35:24.740 --> 35:27.130
-It's really important.
-Okay, I got it.

35:27.170 --> 35:28.090
I'm begging you.

35:28.090 --> 35:28.780
Please find it.

35:28.780 --> 35:31.260
A passenger has lost an item.

35:31.260 --> 35:32.780
It's a keychain

35:33.090 --> 35:35.260
with four Chinese characters on it.

35:47.080 --> 35:47.850
Excuse me.

35:49.580 --> 35:50.630
Yes, sir.

35:52.900 --> 35:54.260
I found a keychain.

35:54.330 --> 35:55.960
It belongs to that girl.

35:56.390 --> 35:58.120
Could you please give it to her?

35:58.410 --> 35:59.510
-There are four Chinese words on it.
-Okay.

35:59.510 --> 36:00.110
Thank you.

36:00.340 --> 36:01.540
It's made of leather.

36:01.610 --> 36:03.090
It says "Zhao and Mu" on it.

36:03.290 --> 36:04.430
If anyone finds it,

36:04.450 --> 36:06.120
please return it to the service desk.

36:06.120 --> 36:06.850
Hello.

36:08.490 --> 36:09.290
Is it this one?

36:11.700 --> 36:12.780
Yes, that's it.

36:13.860 --> 36:14.570
Thank you.

36:14.600 --> 36:15.290
You're welcome.

36:15.290 --> 36:15.960
This is it.

36:15.980 --> 36:16.550
Okay.

36:16.380 --> 36:18.900
[Yearning Day and Night]
